MEV Trading Bot Website (Base Chain)  Goal: Build a modern, professional website for an MEV-aware trading bot on Base, including a marketing landing page and a real-time analytics dashboard. Style similar to Coinbase / Uniswap / Dune Analytics. Dark mode first, transparent and risk-aware.  Page 1: Landing Page Hero  Headline: MEV-Aware Trading Bot for Base Chain  Subheadline: Automated arbitrage & MEV extraction with real-time monitoring  CTAs: Launch Dashboard / View Docs  Visuals: Animated gradient + subtle blockchain animation, 3D trading/robot illustration  Features (3 columns)  Multiple Strategies – Arbitrage, backrunning, liquidation detection  Real-Time Analytics – Mempool monitoring, profit & risk tracking  Gas-Optimized Execution – Smart gas pricing & transaction simulation  How It Works  Monitor → Analyze → Execute → Profit (visual timeline)  Tech Stack  Base, Ethereum, TypeScript, Ethers.js, React, Node.js  Stats  Total transactions  Total profit (USD)  Success rate  Active strategies  CTA  “Ready to Start Extracting MEV?” Button: Access Dashboard Disclaimer: Start on testnet, understand risks  Footer  Docs, GitHub, Discord, Twitter Risk warning + copyright  Page 2: Interactive Dashboard Layout  Left sidebar navigation  Top status bar  Main content area  Top Bar  Bot status (Active/Inactive)  Live Base block number  Wallet balance + address  Dark/Light toggle  Sidebar  Overview · Opportunities · Transactions · Strategies · Performance · Settings  Dashboard Sections Overview  Key metrics: Today’s profit, total txs, active strategies, gas spent  Live opportunities table  Charts: Profit over time, success rate by strategy  Active Opportunities  Filters (strategy, profit, pair, status)  Opportunity cards with profit, gas, risk  Execute / Simulate / Ignore  Side panel with simulation & risk breakdown  Transaction History  Filterable table (tx hash, strategy, profit, gas, status)  Details modal with balances, gas, block, simulation vs actual  Strategies  Cards for Arbitrage / Backrun / Liquidation  Enable/disable, performance stats, mini charts  Configure & backtest modals  Performance Analytics  Time filters (Today → All)  Metrics: profit, win rate, trades, best/worst  Charts: PnL timeline, strategy comparison, gas analysis, pair heatmap  Top trades leaderboard  Settings  General (bot name, theme, notifications)  Network (RPC, WebSocket, status)  Wallet (connect, balances, export)  Risk (limits, stop-loss, emergency stop)  Notifications (Email, Telegram, Discord)  API access (keys, webhooks)  Design System  Colors: Base blue primary, purple accent, green profit, red loss Typography: Inter + JetBrains Mono Components: Dark cards, rounded, subtle borders, animated charts UX: Smooth transitions, counters, skeleton loaders, toasts  Special Features  WebSocket live updates  Interactive charts (zoom, export)  Educational tooltips  Demo mode (mock data)  CSV/PDF exports  Security: session timeout, 2FA, confirmations  Technical Requirements  Mobile-first, WCAG AA accessible  Fast (<2s), SEO landing page  PWA enabled  Code-splitting, lazy loading, virtual lists  Modern browser support